Project Overview:
The purpose of this project is to develop an online platform for customers to purchase and renew vehicle insurance policies. The 

platform will allow customers to:
* Get quotes from multiple insurance providers
* Compare policies and prices
* Purchase a policy online
* Renew a policy online

The platform will also provide customers with access to their policy information, such as their policy number, coverage details, and billing history.

Target Audience : 
The target audience for this project is vehicle owners who are looking for an easy and convenient way to purchase and renew vehicle insurance policies.
The platform will be marketed to customers through online advertising, social media, and word-of-mouth.

Functional Requirements:
The following are the functional requirements for the online vehicle 
insurance platform:
* Customers must be able to get quotes from multiple insurance 
providers.
* Customers must be able to compare policies and prices.
* Customers must be able to purchase a policy online.
* Customers must be able to renew a policy online.
* Customers must be able to access their policy information online.

Non-Functional Requirements:
The following are the non-functional requirements for the online 
vehicle insurance platform :
* The platform must be secure.
* The platform must be reliable.
* The platform must be easy to use.
* The platform must be accessible to users with disabilities

Implementation Plan:
The online vehicle insurance platform will be implemented using a waterfall methodology. The project will be divided into the following phases:
* Requirements gathering
* Design
* Development
* Testing
* Deployment

Testing Plan:
The online vehicle insurance platform will be tested using a combination of unit testing, integration testing, and system testing. Unit testing will be performed by the development team to 
ensure that each individual unit of code works as expected. Integration testing will be performed to ensure that the different units of code work together correctly. System testing will be 
performed to ensure that the entire platform meets all of the functional and non-functional requirements.

Deployment Plan
The online vehicle insurance platform will be deployed to a cloud-based server. The server will be hosted by a reputable hosting provider.
The platform will be accessible to customers through a web browser.
Maintenance Plan
The online vehicle insurance platform will be maintained by a team of software engineers. The maintenance team will be responsible for fixing bugs, adding new features, and 
updating the platform to keep it up-to-date with the latest security standards.
This is just a sample business requirement specification for an online vehicle insurance project. The specific requirements for your project may vary depending on the specific needs of your business 
and your target audience.
